{"title":"Rapha’s New Eyewear for 2024","link":"https://theradavist.com/raphas-new-eyewear-for-2024/","date":1711029495000,"content":"<p><img width=\"1844\" height=\"1032\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/unnamed-6.png?fit=1200,1032&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/unnamed-6.png?w=1844&amp;quality=75 1844w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/unnamed-6.png?resize=1200,672&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/unnamed-6.png?resize=768,430&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/unnamed-6.png?resize=1536,860&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /><span></span></p>\n<p>Rapha has produced some exceptional eyewear over the years and <a href=\"https://www.rapha.cc/us/en_US/eyewear/category/glasses\" target=\"_blank\">2024’s offerings</a> spring into the riding season with three performance models…</p>\n<p><img width=\"1285\" height=\"858\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/Rapha_Eyewear_2024.jpg?fit=1200,858&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/Rapha_Eyewear_2024.jpg?w=1285&amp;quality=75 1285w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/Rapha_Eyewear_2024.jpg?resize=1200,801&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/Rapha_Eyewear_2024.jpg?resize=768,513&amp;quality=75 768w\" /></p>\n<p>The <a href=\"https://www.rapha.cc/us/en_US/shop/letras-glasses/product/BNK01XXBLR\" target=\"_blank\">Letras</a> ($205) and <a href=\"https://www.rapha.cc/us/en_US/shop/reis-glasses/product/BMF01XXBLR\" target=\"_blank\">Reis</a> ($205) are sporty silhouettes, falling in line with current eyewear designs. The main difference between the two being the Reis feature a solid frame across the top of the lens while the Letras are frameless. Perhaps the most unique offering from Rapha to date, however, are the <a href=\"https://www.rapha.cc/us/en_US/shop/dalton-glasses/product/BNM01XXBMI\" target=\"_blank\">Dalton</a> ($180), which take inspiration from cycling’s rich history with oval lenses from Briko to Oakley and feature an integrated strap on the arms. </p>\n<p>See the full lineup at Rapha.  </p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/raphas-new-eyewear-for-2024/\">Rapha’s New Eyewear for 2024</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://theradavist.com\">The Radavist</a>.</p>","author":"John Watson","siteTitle":"The Radavist","siteHash":"96eb481d8084f04a4602bac57874ba717baf56b758f45547b5caf2312da766ef","entryHash":"3084a59b296efbefe8256d51839fd0fdecdce3c326b48a1e69f410b56d7bb5a2","category":"Cycling"}